The President of Russia Vladimir Putin signed law about the introduction to the administrative responsibilities for the violation of period and order of the payment of goods (works, services) with the realization of purchases for the state and municipal needs.
This law is called to solve the very acute problem of the nonfulfillment of its obligations by customers with the realization of state and municipal purchases.
Already two years ago the situation, when owners could not obtain payment for the already completed state and municipal contracts, was general.
At the same time the President of Russia gave commission to the General Procurator's office RF to take problem for the special control.
Because businessmen themselves could not manage the unconscientious customers, who concluded the not reinforced by financing contracts, in every way possible attempted to deviate from the undertaken obligations on the payment and were included in agreements illegal conditions.
Problem was system as a whole in the country.
Since 2015 in the interests of the protection of the rights of owners to obtaining of payment for public orders the prosecutor's office introduced 9,700 ideas, according to the results of their examination to the disciplinary responsibility are drawn 4,500 officials, to the administrative - 533, into the investigation organs for organizing the processual checkings are represented 75 materials, the criminal cases are excited on 46 of them.
Was as a result extinguished debts before the owners for sum more than 66 billion rubles.
Moreover these enormous sums were accumulated by no means not as a result of neoplaty of multibillion contracts.
Numerous, systematic delays on the payment of services to owners for far the more modest sums led to the legendary debts.
Here is the characteristic case.
The leader of small company won competition to the rendering of services on the social transportation by several million rubles.
Man put all his circulating capital, completely fulfilled obligations, but the assumed money in time not obtained.
Result - increasing financial kilohms from the debts on the wages, taxes, credits, which would lead to bankruptcy, if owner did not turn for help into the prosecutor's office.
Now in a number of regions it was possible to maximally level problem.
Nevertheless as of the first half-year of 2017 the joint volume of debt on the state and municipal contracts, revealed by the attorneys of the subjects of the Russian Federation, was about 27.4 billion rubles.
In the regions, where the indices of debts continue to reach critical values, the prosecutor's office works in the mode of manual anticrisis control.
Attorney General personally carries out visiting conferences with the representatives of the local authority, on which objectively are investigated all revealed by attorneys disturbances and measures for their immediate elimination.
Such operational conferences in this year already took place in Yaroslavl' and Ekaterinburg.
To qualitatively improve pay discipline of public customers will be able the realization of the federal law of № 189-FZ “about the introduction of changes in the code of the Russian Federation about the administrative offenses in the part of the establishment of the administrative responsibilities of the officials of customer for the violation of period and order of the payment of goods (works, services) with the realization of purchases for guaranteeing the state and municipal needs”, which the President of Russia last week signed.
The project of law was developed the Ministry of Economic Development of Russia on the initiative of the Attorney General's Office.
New law will supplement the code of the Russian Federation about the administrative offenses with the article, which provides for penalty from 30,000 to 50,000 rubles for the disturbance by the official of the customer of period and order of the payment of goods, works and services with the state and municipal purchases.
But if official already underwent administrative punishment for the similar offense, then disqualification for the period from one year to two years waits it.
All attorneys of the subjects of the Russian Federation already obtained commission to ensure the application of these legislative short stories in practice.
