About the fact that the managing director of east and deputy of the director general of TSENKI for technological development Andrey Okhlopkov turned to the work in the State Research and Production Space Center of the name of Khrunichev, “"” described the top managers of several enterprises of the space industry, and also colleague of the apparatus of government.
“It works at the new post already several weeks”, specified collocutors “"” in the branch.
On Thursday it was impossible to obtain the operational commentary of TSENKI, but Mr. himself Okhlopkov for the commentaries was inaccessible.
However, information “"” they officially confirmed in the State Research and Production Space Center.
It made a decision about the passage to the post of director for the coordination of production, they stated at the enterprise. - Andrey Okhlopkov the assigned to it task in the guarantee of the starting minimum for the first starting at the spaceport east completely carried out.
Mr. Okhlopkov passed to the work in TSENKI in 2013, having after the arms a service in the space troops, in particular in Baikonur, and in Plesetsk - at “northern” spaceport it occupied the post of the first deputy of commander in the title of Colonel.
In 2009 Andrey Okhlopkov became the pretender of criminal case.
Consequence accused it of the bribery: allegedly from its supply regional traders obtained for the recoils state orders, but did not carry out the undertaken obligations in the harvesting of the detachable parts of the launch vehicles in the Arkhangyelsk province and republic of the Komi.
In 2012 the judgment of jurors recognized as its innocent.
Responsibilities for technological development entrusted to it in TSENKI applied to different projects, but construction in the spaceport in the Far East became the main things of them.
Headed then federal Space Agency Oleg Ostapenko in the interview “"” directly said that the position of the matters on east “was critical already in October 2013”.
The fact is that during the planning the strategic error was committed: the completion of building and conducting the first start of launch vehicle “Soyuz-2.1” were planned to one and the same period - the end of 2015.
In order to accomplish launching before the end of the year, they decided to complete building to half a year earlier and periods displaced since December in July 2015.
For accelerating the process it was necessary to go to craftiness: the specialists of TSENKI began to conduct parallel assembly of technological equipment on the unfinished objects.
The chief supporter of this idea was Andrey Okhlopkov.
In spite of the existed risks and nevertheless happened transfer (instead of December 2015 " Soyuz " it flew away only on April 28, 2016), this idea justified itself, speaks source “"” at the spaceport: “Otherwise we, until now, carried out not one launching from east, but they would be occupied by building”.
Vice-Premier Dmitriy Rogozin, who treats the creation of spaceport, into the joke called Andrey Okhlopkova by his “space Susanin”, but in it almost always he precisely inquired information about the motion of building.
Was memorized Mr. Okhlopkov and by the straightness: for example, in the interview “"” he proposed to deprive Federal agency for the special building (special-build) of status of only executor on east and directly to work with the subcontractors: “Why we must all eggs add into one basket of special-system?”
This idea found support in the government.
Since 2017 TSENKI took upon itself the responsibilities of general contractor in order to launchings the planned in the fourth quarter to complete construction-assembly works on the launch and technical complex.
According to the data “"”, occasion for passing Mr. Okhlopkov in the new place of work became the differences with the leadership TSENKI relative to the methods of the completion of building construction and complexes of spaceport, and also methods of operation with the subcontractural organizations.
“It was solved, which so will be better for all”, says one of the top managers, of participating in the erection east.
The colleague of the apparatus of government, in turn, calls the solution strange: “He was one of the best specialists, to find to him equivalent replacement will be complex”.
According to the data “"”, this and it will not be required: the post of the technical director of spaceport will be abolished, and its functions will be scattered on the subdivisions of TSENKI.
