To disabled to Anton to Mamaev was appointed the penalty
Moscow City Court softened punishment to disabled-carriage maker to Anton to Mamaev from four and one-half of the years of the deprivation of freedom to the penalty into 200,000 rub
By the previously decision of Timiryzevskiy of court that condemned was freed from SIZO (Detention Facility).
In this case Moscow City Court confirmed that accused is criminal, since organized the robbery and theft of motor scooter in the former fighter of the Special Force.
Moscow City Court by its solution softened punishment to Anton to Mamaev to 200,000 rub of penalty.
“Mamaev is the organizer of robbery, which also forms the composition of crime, and, correspondingly, this face must be drawn to the criminal responsibility”, explained “"” press-secretary Moscow City Court Ulyan Solopova.
In this case by court it was taken into account the status of the health of Mamaev, actual circumstances of the matter, absence of the aggravating circumstances.
Furthermore, court used st. 64 Criminal Code of the Russian Federation, according to which it is possible to appoint the punishment of lower than the lowest limit.
As far as the assistant of Mamaev Vasiliy Seroshtanova is concerned, court did not establish the circumstances, which would become base for changing the category of gravity of that effected and change in the sentence.
Anton himself Mamaev stated that he remained dissatisfied by the solution of Moscow City Court.
I am disappointed by Court decision.
By unique legal solution there would be justification, it was intended further to be beaten for justice.
Its attorney Andrey Orlov did not exclude the appeal of sentence in the appeal instance of Moscow City Court and Supreme Court.
“We will use all levers up to the European Court of Human Rights”, he stated “Russian International News Agency”.
Let us recall, 28-year-old Muscovite Anton Mamaev, which suffers spinal muscular atrophy, became the pretender of criminal case last fall.
Disabled asserts that purchased the motor scooter in acquaintances for 160,000 rub, in order then to sell.
However, the owners of motor scooter, among whom - the former fighter of the Special Force, they stated that the disabled and his assistant Vasiliy Seroshtanov selected in them property, threatening to use violence.
On June 30 Timiryzevskiy the district court of Moscow sentenced Vasiliy Seroshtanova to three years of colony, and Anton of Mamaev - to four and one-half to the years of the deprivation of freedom with the serving of punishment in the penal colony (on h. of 2 st. 162 Criminal Code of the Russian Federation).
After the immobilized disabled was placed in SIZO (Detention Facility), to the matter were connected the Public Chamber, Attorney General's Office, authorized on human rights with the President Tatiana Moskalkova.
As a result, in the middle of July Anton Mamaev was freed from SIZO (Detention Facility) by the solution of the same Timiryzevskiy court.
Protection, in turn, appealed the solution of the first instance in Moscow City Court.
