In Russia will appear two new territories of the anticipating social and economic development - “Abaza” and “Novotroitsk”.
The corresponding decisions of government RF will come into force today, on August 4.
Are determined boundaries and forms of economic activity of Thor in the territory of Abaza city in the republic Khakassia.
In the city, where live 15,000 people, will act the special legal regime of owner's activity, and also minimum volume of the capital investments of residents, minimum quantity of new constant jobs.
It is assumed that this 2.5 billion rubles in the investments will draw into city on the order of, and more than 600 new jobs will be also created.
In the enumeration of the forms of economic activity, with which into Thor “Abaza” will act the special legal regime of owner's activity, for example, included plant growing, stock raising, the production of food, nonalcoholic beverages and clothing.
Even now the government of republic signed frame agreements about the realization of 8 investment projects.
Also it is planned to decrease the dependence of territory on the town-forming enterprise in LLC (Limited liability company) “Abakan mine”.
In January 2017 the authorities of region reported that Khakassia satisfied all conditions of the Ministry of Economic Development for the creation Thor.
Similarly entered the authorities of Orenburg region.
There, in Novotroitsk city will be also created the territory of the anticipating social and economic development.
This will make it possible to diversify the economy of mono-city, to decrease its dependence on the town-forming enterprise AO “Ural steel”, and to also create more than 2,300 jobs and to draw investment in the volume are more than 8 mmilliardov of rubles.
In the enumeration of the forms of economic activity, with which in the new Thor will act special legal regime for the owners, are included, in particular, fresh-water fish-breeding, production of fodders, medicines and medical materials.
Novotroitsk became the first of the mono-cities of Orenburg region, that received status Thor.
Let us recall that the territory of the anticipating development - this is the economic zone with the privilege tax conditions, simplified by the administrative procedures and other privileges, which is created for the attraction of investitsiyi of an improvement in the life of population.
Among the privileges for the residents Thor it is possible to isolate the following: tax on profit in the size not more than 5% for the first five years, and is not less than 10% for the following 5 years, social payments in size of 7.6% for 10 years, the use of a regime of free customs zone, the privilege regime of connection to different objects of infrastructure, or privilege rates on the lease pay.
